{"type": "article", "id": 12740, "title": "Converse Chuck Taylor All Star II", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-29T06:36:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122500Ky5ue0rxNawg8BSj.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tConverse 进来发布全新 Chuck Taylor All Star II 系列，是 1917 年经典的 Chuck Taylor All Star 系列的全面革新。新的系列在外观上基本维持了其经典作品的特色，但在制作技术上，首次运用了 Nike Lunarlon 技术，为鞋底极大增强了减震和支撑功能。以前经常受到诟病的鞋侧易开胶的问题，在这次的革新中得到了重视，新的音波压纹技术投入使用，增强了鞋侧胶条的耐用程度。新的系列有黑，白，红，蓝四种配色可以选择，目前已经登陆 Converse 线上商店，这是<a href=\"http://www.converse.com.cn/chuckII.htm\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404346Nmt9I45Sr8UTLiH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140434KA1v6CjcmBrpGkRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140435OoNI4tlGSfKnJFCe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6518847\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140435HsZNuOyeQ5IBgUfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66457023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140436zbrOQ3W8cGCgkm4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83166333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140436zPSFsENDpyT2XZUo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140437G8JwOcdDrPvR0Aoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140438idnh8l5fNpqHVWGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67524752\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140439GtQ6Ii51HJFso3Sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}